<br>
1st I thought I wanted to be Non- KOS to Giants so I killed coldain, and Coldain wolves. This took me to Threatingly to Giants, and KOS to Thrug. After about 3 days of casual soloing the giant fort in GD ( Run in the front door, and work my way around back tot he front, new spawns in place by then.) I am currently Amiable to Coldain and threatingly to CoV, I figure maybe 1 more day tops for Non-KOS status. But you can do all the raids you want, but as for the quwstion at hand, that is how I, as a solo only mage, am getting my CoV faction.<br>
